      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "COMPUTE (1) broke through for his maiden success last time out at Ballarat over 450m (25.11). Ran one of the fastest times on the program in his latest win. Well placed and will be tough to beat. DEVINGTON (7) comes here after a sizzling Mix 6/7 win at Bendigo over 425m in 23.85. Should be in this for a long way. HOPPY (8) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (22.26) at Ballarat in Grade 7 over 390m. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Will go close again if runs up to latest. HARD LAUNCH (6) showed good early speed and won on debut. That form reads well.",
